Clair Schuler is a drag queen who was friends with Robert Durst when he was pretending to be a deaf, mute woman . 
  The 71-year-old real estate tycoon used to live on Galveston Island and went by the name of Dorothy in the early 2000s . 
  Schuler said Durst was fascinated with wigs and make-up . 
  He said he was not fooled by Durst's apparent deafness . 
  He was 'infatuated with the drag queens that performed and even carried a tablet to communicate his thoughts' Durst is facing the death penalty in California for murdering his friend Susan Berman in 2000 . 
 